details.name: Primal Split
details.description: Splits Brewmaster into elements, forming 3 specialized warriors, adept at survival. If any of them survive until the end of their summoned timer, the Brewmaster is reborn. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Earth gains Thunder Clap, Storm gains Cinder Brew and Fire gains Drunken Brawler.
